## Easy way to get neovim setup ; 

mkdir -p ~/.config/nvim ; mkdir -p ~/.config/nvim/autoload/ ; curl -Lo ~/.config/nvim/autoload/plug.vim https://raw.githubusercontent.com/junegunn/vim-plug/master/plug.vim ; curl -Lo ~/.config/nvim/init.vim https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chris5692/nvim/master/init.vim ; nvim -c PlugInstall 
